インタフェースの使用
org.sxb.kit.MultiValueMap

  • MultiValueMapを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.sxb.http
    包含了客户端/服务器端的HTTP基本抽象类 用于Restful
    Contains a basic abstraction over client/server-side HTTP.
    org.sxb.http.converter
    Provides an HttpMessageConverter abstraction to convert between Java objects and HTTP input/output messages.
    org.sxb.kit
    SXB预置工具类包
    已经包含当今非常流行的工具,请尽量优先使用此包中的工具
    org.sxb.upload.ext.multipart
    commons fileupload跟Servlet3.0内置上传功能的包装与实现 Multipart resolution framework for handling file uploads.
    org.sxb.upload.ext.multipart.support
    Support classes for the multipart resolution framework.
    org.sxb.web.util
    本包中类尚未启用，后续版本开发预留

      修飾子とタイプ クラスと説明
      class  HttpHeaders
      Represents HTTP request and response headers, mapping string header names to list of string values.
      MultiValueMap型のパラメータを持つorg.sxb.httpのコンストラクタ 
      コンストラクタと説明
      HttpEntity(MultiValueMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> headers)
      Create a new HttpEntity with the given headers and no body.
      HttpEntity(T body, MultiValueMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> headers)
      Create a new HttpEntity with the given body and headers.
      RequestEntity(MultiValueMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> headers, HttpMethod method, java.net.URI url)
      Constructor with method, URL and headers but without body.
      RequestEntity(T body, MultiValueMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> headers, HttpMethod method, java.net.URI url)
      Constructor with method, URL, headers and body.
      ResponseEntity(MultiValueMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> headers, HttpStatus statusCode)
      Create a new HttpEntity with the given headers and status code, and no body.
      ResponseEntity(T body, MultiValueMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> headers, HttpStatus statusCode)
      Create a new HttpEntity with the given body, headers, and status code.

      多值映射Map
